/on_cancel (RTO flow)
Default RTO flow will be for "RTO-Disposed", i.e. without return:
if the RTO request is valid (as determined by the reason code and other info provided), LBNP has to accept the request;
for on-network logistics, /on_cancel will also result in cascaded retail /on_cancel request, for the fulfillment, and include the new fulfillment record for RTO, fulfillment start location / time, fulfillment state, order state, etc;
Flow for RTO, with return, is coveredhere;
