Other baseline features - 000
Other baseline features include:
Updated flow for RTO
Updated flow for RTO
Separate fulfillment[306]will be created for RTO (type = "RTO");
Forward shipment fulfillment will be linked to RTO fulfillment using "rto_event";
Since LSPs track a single shipment status for forward shipment / RTO:
set forward shipment fulfillment to terminal state ("RTO[307]");
fulfillment state for RTO fulfillment will be updated to "RTO-Initiated";
Order quote will be updated to include RTO cost before order / RTO fulfillment reaches terminal state;
Terminal state for RTO fulfillment is"RTO-Delivered" or "RTO-Disposed";[ag][ah]
Terminal state for order is "Completed" when RTO fulfillment is updated to terminal state;
Others
Others
Settlement window & settlement terms to be provided, for the order, by payment collector;
For P2H2P shipments, the shipment type ("flyer", "box") will be used to compute the weight for pricing:
"flyer": if dead weight < 1 kg, use dead weight else max(dead weight,  volumetric weight);
"box": max(dead weight,  volumetric weight)
for"box"shipment type, weight for pricing = max(dead weight,  volumetric weight). If the box dimensions are large, it will take a lot of space and handling at the logistic end, e.g.:
seller sends 500g shipment (dead weight) with 22x20x18cm dimension box;
volumetric weight is 1.5kg (22*20*18/5000[ai][aj][ak]);
hence, weight for pricing is 1.5kg;
