Updated flow for Immediate Delivery - 000
LSP performs mandatory inline check for rider and sends info in "inline_check_for_rider" (/on_init);
LBNPmustsend following information as part of order/confirm:
estimate of order preparation time
"ready_to_ship" = "yes"
reference retail order id
static OTP for pickup / delivery verification (optional, as required)
LBNP should use their estimate of order preparation time & estimate of time to pickup (by LSP) to decide when to place the logistics order;
LSP may NACK /confirm if:
conditions in 1 aren’t met - LSP can NACK /confirm with error code 65005;
if rider isn’t available, LSP can NACK /confirm with error code 60004;
When order is ready, LBNP sends "order_ready"="yes" (/update);
Ridermustset fulfillment state to "At-pickup", after reaching the perimeter of the pickup location (/on_status);
