Quick commerce / milk run /SPMD logistics[ap][aq]- 005, 006, 007
LBNP sends /search request, with params such as:
no of orders or riders;
pickup location;
pickup & delivery slot;
max motorable distance for serviceability;
rate basis (rate per rider or order):
LSP sends /on_search response, with response for search params as above:
LSP quotes 2 price components, as per rate basis - base price (min guarantee amount), additional price in case the original t&c are breached;
for RTO, the cost will be determined based on additional price component, e.g. for extra rider time or extra order;
Wherever pickup & delivery slots are provided, ready_to_ship is not applicable;
Since this is bulk shipment flow, the logistics order will be tracked through the following fulfillments:
template fulfillment- identified byfulfillment.type = "Batch", for terms & conditions, as provided in /search params above;
retail fulfillment- for each retail order being delivered;
Flows for milk run logistics (006),SPMD (007)[ar][as]will be similar to Quick commerce logistics, with different category:
Quick commerce logistics uses category "Instant Delivery" (with S2D TAT, etc. as defined below);
Milk run logistics, SPMD may use existing categories "Immediate Delivery", "Same Day Delivery", "Next Day Delivery", as defined here;
