Pre-order flow
Pre-order flow
Following are possible scenarios:
LBNP requested fororder_countno of orders for delivery - flow sequenced as below:
LBNP updates order delivery details (along with other info inlinked_order), when available (thru /init, /confirm or /update), for the corresponding retail fulfillment;
LBNP requested forrider_countno of riders - flow below may not necessarily be in sequence:
LBNP updates order delivery details (along with other info inlinked_order), when available (thru /init, /confirm or /update), for the corresponding retail fulfillment:
if delivery details aren’t available in /init, LBNP may use thetemplate fulfillmentto communicate pickup location & other information to LSP;
rider details will be communicated by LSP using thetemplate fulfillment;
after communicating all rider details, LSP may update thetemplate fulfillmentstate to "Agent-assigned";
LBNP shall assign rider to each retail fulfillment (based on rider details from LSP) and LSP updates the retail fulfillment state to "Agent-assigned";
LSP communicates rider information to LBNP; subsequent to this, LBNP updates agent details, for each fulfillment, and communicates to LSP using /update;
In both the above scenarios, LSP will assign fulfillment id to each fulfillment;[bj][bk][bl]
