COD order - 008
Proposed flow for COD orders:
LBNP declares COD order & collection amount in search intent;
LSP publishes COD capability for courier (checkhere), collection charge;
LSP specifies payment terms for logistics order & linked retail order;
since payment terms for the logistics order & the linked retail order could be different, payment terms, status, timestamps for the logistics & linked retail orders will be maintained separately;
payment for logistics order = forward shipment cost & tax + collection charge & tax;
in case of RTO, collection charge will be 0;
LBNP provides settlement details for deposit of retail order value;
