FIFO order - 00C
LBNP sends /search intent, with params such as:
pickup location;
pickup slot;
max motorable distance for serviceability;
(static) OTP;
No retail order details, e.g. delivery location, etc. in /search intent;
LSP sends their catalog with or without the rate card;
FIFO order is always for 1 retail order, where a rider is requested and then any retail order can be assigned:
LBNP assigns a rider who scans static OTP at pickup ("At-Pickup");
LBNP assigns retail order details anytime before pickup - retail order details, delivery location, pickup bin location;
