Payment wallet - 00D
Prepaid payment for logistics can be enabled through the payment wallet maintained by LSP for an LBNP;
Creation & maintenance of the payment wallet will be handled off-network, i.e. LSP may create the wallet for LBNP during dynamic onboarding, communicate the same to LBNP using contact details provided over the protocol & LBNP refreshes balance as needed;
Current wallet balance can also be provided by LSP, for payment type of "ON-ORDER", when LBNP requests for quote;
Wallet will be auto-debited for the logistics transaction:
Blocking of wallet balance in /on_init;
Auto-debit of wallet balance in /on_confirm;
Due to insufficient wallet balance, LSP can reject confirmation of order with appropriate error code;
For cancellation, wallet balance auto-debit has to be reversed;
