Cancellation terms - 01A
Cancellation terms may be defined by LSP during pre-order flow:
apply to cancellation by LSP or LBNP;
definition is at the fulfillment level and based on the fulfillment state & reason codes and includes associated cancellation fees (if any):
cancellation fees for order cancellation will be the aggregate of cancellation fees for individual fulfillments;
if cancellation terms are not acceptable to LBNP, they may NACK the /on_init or /on_confirm callback, with error code 62505;
Actual cancellation fees are reflected in the order quote after cancellation of fulfillment or order;
