Differential weight charges - 021
LSP notifies LBNP of differential weight charges:
LSP to provide the differential cost, taxes on differential cost, updated weight & dimensions;
can be provided thru unsolicited /on_update or /on_status;
for weight differential impacting RTO costs, LSP to provide the same info in /on_cancel;
LBNP response to differential weight charges:
if LBNP ACKs, it means they accept the updated quote, including the weight differential cost;
in this case, the differential cost will be added to total forward shipment cost & may also be reflected in cancellation fees, for cases where the order is subsequently cancelled;
if LBNP doesn’t accept the differential cost, they can NACK /on_update (with error code 62504); in this case, the LSP should revert the proposed changes in quote, order weight & dimensions and subsequent action will be as per the terms & conditions agreed upon between the LBNP & LSP;
